tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Worn_Equipment\" title=\"Worn Equipment\">Equipable</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">No</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Stackable_items\" title=\"Stackable items\">Stackable</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">No</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Note\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Note\">Noteable</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">Yes</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Destroy\" title=\"Destroy\">Destroy</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">Drop</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Examine\" title=\"Examine\">Examine</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">A scale from the hide of a lava dragon.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Values</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Value\" title=\"Value\">Value</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">50 coins</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/High_Level_Alchemy\" title=\"High Level Alchemy\">High alch</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">30 coins</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Low_Level_Alchemy\" title=\"Low Level Alchemy\">Low alch</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">20 coins</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Weight\" title=\"Weight\">Weight</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">0.01 kg</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Grand Exchange</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/RuneScape:Grand_Exchange_Market_Watch\" title=\"RuneScape:Grand Exchange Market Watch\">Exchange</a></th><td colspan=\"13\"><span class=\"infobox-quantity\" data-val-each=\"1555\"><span class=\"infobox-quantity-replace\">1,555</span> coins (<a href=\"/w/Exchange:Lava_scale\" title=\"Exchange:Lava scale\">info</a>)</span></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Grand_Exchange#Buy_limits\" title=\"Grand Exchange\">Buy limit</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">11,000</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Grand_Exchange#Volume\" title=\"Grand Exchange\">Daily volume</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">1,063</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-full-width-content\"><div class=\"realtimePrices\" style=\"display: none;\" data-itemid=\"11992\"></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-full-width-content\"><div class=\"GEChartBox\"><div class=\"GEChartItems\" style=\"display:none\"></div><div class=\"GEdatachart smallChart\" style=\"height:160px;margin:0 auto;width:258px\"><div style=\"user-select:none;opacity:.75;text-align:center;font-size:.9em\">Loading...</div></div><div class=\"GEdataprices\" data-item=\"Lava scale\" data-itemid=\"11992\" data-limit=\"11000\" data-value=\"50\" style=\"display:none\"></div></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Advanced data</th></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"7\">Item ID</th><td colspan=\"13\">11992</td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"infobox-smw-data\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\n<div class=\"floatleft\"><a href=\"/w/File:Lava_scale_detail.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Lava scale detail.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Lava_scale_detail.png/150px-Lava_scale_detail.png?95df4\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"150\" height=\"138\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Lava_scale_detail.png/225px-Lava_scale_detail.png?95df4 1.5x, /images/thumb/Lava_scale_detail.png/300px-Lava_scale_detail.png?95df4 2x\" data-file-width=\"711\" data-file-height=\"652\" /></a></div>\n<p><b>Lava scales</b> are always dropped by <a href=\"/w/Lava_dragon\" title=\"Lava dragon\">lava dragons</a> at the <a href=\"/w/Lava_Dragon_Isle\" title=\"Lava Dragon Isle\">Lava Dragon Isle</a> located in the <a href=\"/w/Wilderness\" title=\"Wilderness\">Wilderness</a>. They are also dropped uncommonly by <a href=\"/w/Brutal_black_dragon\" title=\"Brutal black dragon\">brutal black dragons</a>. The shards are an ingredient for <a href=\"/w/Extended_antifire\" title=\"Extended antifire\">extended antifire</a> and <a href=\"/w/Extended_super_antifire\" title=\"Extended super antifire\">extended super antifire</a> potions.\n</p><p>Lava scales themselves have no use, but when ground with a <a href=\"/w/Pestle_and_mortar\" title=\"Pestle and mortar\">pestle and mortar</a>, players will obtain 3-6 <a href=\"/w/Lava_scale_shard\" title=\"Lava scale shard\">lava scale shards</a>, or 6-9 with the completion of the <a href=\"/w/Wilderness_Diary#Hard\" title=\"Wilderness Diary\">Hard Wilderness Diary</a>. The amount is random, with high <a href=\"/w/Herblore\" title=\"Herblore\">Herblore</a> level yielding a higher average.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> With 99 Herblore, players almost always receive the maximum amount with a rare chance of getting fewer.\n</p><p>If asking <a href=\"/w/Wesley\" title=\"Wesley\">Wesley</a> to grind them, he can only crush one scale to three shards, warning the player of this before proceeding.\n</p><p>Note: If attempting to obtain lava scale shards, <a href=\"/w/Infernal_eel\" title=\"Infernal eel\">Infernal eel</a> fishing is a viable option for players wishing to avoid the wilderness.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en-GB\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Products\